Package com.views

package com.views
  • Class
    Description
    GuestViews
    The class that provides the API for the presentation layer interacting with the user to get input for operations on the Guest Object.
    MenuViews
    The class that provides the API for the presentation layer interacting with the user to get input for operations on the MenuItem Object.
    PaymentViews
    The class that provides the API for the presentation layer interacting with the user to get input for Payment operations.
    ReservationViews
    The class that provides the API for the presentation layer interacting with the user to get input for operations on the Reservation Object.
    RoomServiceViews
    The class that provides the API for the presentation layer interacting with the user to get input for the Room Service feature.
    RoomViews
    The class that provides the API for the presentation layer interacting with the user to get input on generating summaries on Room data and updating Room Statuses.
    UserInputViews
    The class that provides the API for the presentation layer to get appropriate user input.
    Views
    An interface that enforces that all Views APIs have a process method for their respective core functionalities
